{"tid":422464,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"廣東話使用人數真係每年都跌緊","createTime":"2017-10-03T05:38:32.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-04T05:15:28.000Z","uid":123034,"like":11,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":40,"replies":[{"pid":"dc380ae62af07fcc20e18aa4326cc5b115e6bf1d","tid":422464,"uid":123034,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T05:38:32.000Z","msg":"啱啱入cia個網check下香港語言使用率方面，廣東話跌到89%，我記得前年睇過有92%<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n今次真係仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.cia.gov/library/publications/resources/the-world-factbook/geos/hk.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cia.gov%2Flibrary%2Fpublications%2Fresources%2Fthe-world-factbook%2Fgeos%2Fhk.html&d=hSaw7YAqDoR7w%2BFi8M%2FsyjPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=90b97c8d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.cia.gov/library/publications/resources/the-world-factbook/geos/hk.html</a>"},{"pid":"87d39a124978507adb0f6d1369e5e16d60d08f45","tid":422464,"uid":121744,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T05:46:03.000Z","msg":"一早知"},{"pid":"26a7342daa85faf7893970c991cca5bf91c2f741","tid":422464,"uid":53223,"like":1,"dislike":55,"score":-54,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T06:01:25.000Z","msg":"未來根本就應該推英文推普通話"},{"pid":"345a67c804f1f8f7129212480bae8b04b4121319","tid":422464,"uid":41245,"like":8,"dislike":11,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T06:06:32.000Z","msg":"香港人仲俾失敗主義撚帶走講緊獨立有冇可能性<br />\n俾踩港撚帶走踩香港多港豬<br />\n成個民族性變晒失敗主義<br />\n咪冇人出嚟囉，俾失敗主義洗版，個個覺得自己係少數，冇晒團結力量<br />\n以前有人出嚟反蝗語，好多香港人都好支持<br />\n依家香港人就同失敗主義撚一齊講「換血啦！香港冇得救」<br />\n失敗主義根本就係癌細胞"},{"pid":"7e0b13d98557bfcd710868d6eafb7a9ef3cd716d","tid":422464,"uid":38671,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T06:07:10.000Z","msg":"越來越多細路用普通話傾計"},{"pid":"595547f64ec91d3d249f8fc04ae011f738c8037d","tid":422464,"uid":426,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0